@NODE "Introduction" "Introduction"
@{PARI 0}@{LINDENT 0}@{PAR}@{JCENTER}@{BG FILL}[ @{" Contents " LINK "main"} @{" WB use " LINK "Atelier"} @{" Tool types settings " LINK "Optic¶ne"} @{" Address " LINK "Adresse"} ]@{BG BACK}@{LINE}
@{PI}
@{b}Convaski@{ub} converts Ascii files from one character set to another.@{PAR}
@{b}Convaski@{ub} is written in E, version 2.1b.@{PAR}
If you're looking for references in conversion tables, look at
ftp://unicode.org, or http://www.unicode.org.@{PAR}

@{PARI 0}@{LINDENT 0}@{PAR}@{JCENTER}@{BG FILL}[ @{" Contents " LINK "main"} @{" WB use " LINK "Atelier"} @{" Tool types settings " LINK "Optic¶ne"} @{" Address " LINK "Adresse"} ]@{BG BACK}@{LINE}

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Besoin" "What do I need?"
@{PARI 0}@{LINDENT 0}@{PAR}@{JCENTER}@{BG FILL}[ @{" Contents " LINK "main"} @{" WB use " LINK "Atelier"} @{" Tool types settings " LINK "Optic¶ne"} @{" Address " LINK "Adresse"} ]@{BG BACK}@{LINE}
@{PI}
Convaski needs:@{PAR}
@{LINDENT 8}@{PARI -4}
-- an Amiga (of course. . .),@{PAR}
-- Workbench 2.0 or superior,@{PAR}
-- CrossDos-like program to communicate with the PC and Macintosh worlds or
CrossMac if you're only interested in Macintosh (but it's a commercial product).

@{PARI 0}@{LINDENT 0}@{PAR}@{JCENTER}@{BG FILL}[ @{" Contents " LINK "main"} @{" WB use " LINK "Atelier"} @{" Tool types settings " LINK "Optic¶ne"} @{" Address " LINK "Adresse"} ]@{BG BACK}

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Atelier" "Workbench use"
@{PARI 0}@{LINDENT 0}@{PAR}@{JCENTER}@{BG FILL}[ @{" Contents " LINK "main"} @{b} WB use @{ub} @{" Tool types settings " LINK "Optic¶ne"} @{" Address " LINK "Adresse"} ]@{BG BACK}@{LINE}
@{PI}
You can put Convaski where you want. As the default language is English, you do
not need the drawer named Catalogs (French and Spanish translations).@{PAR}
When you double-click on the Convaski icon, you can see several buttons and
gadgets. Here is the description of their use.@{PAR}
@{CODE}
_________________________________
@{"ñ" LINK "BFermer"} Convaski 3.0                @{"Z" LINK "BZoom"}O
---------------------------------
@{" Help... " LINK "BAide"}  @{" About..." LINK "BApropos"}  @{"  Quit   " LINK "BQuitter"}
@{" Open... " LINK "BOuvrir"}  @{"  View   " LINK "BVoir"}  @{" Convert " LINK "BComm"}
Direction:  @{"C|   Amiga -> Mac   " LINK "BSens"}
Memory:     @{"C|     Maximal      " LINK "BMÕmoire"}
Viewer:     @{"sys:utilities/more  " LINK "BAfficheur"}
@{"  " LINK "BGuill"} Curved quotes      @{"  " LINK "BAuto"} Auto
From  @{"                        " LINK "BDeVers"} @{"i" LINK "BI"}
To    @{"                        " LINK "BDeVers"} @{"d" LINK "BT"}
₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤₤

_________________________________
Convaski 3.0                  @{"Z" LINK "BZoom"}O
---------------------------------
@{"                               " LINK "BFichier"}
